    "This is not surprising as these terms are methods for TM/ algorithms.",
    "• Figure 10 (in appendix) shows the terms in cluster 2 and can be profiled as \"Information mining\".",
    "This is because the cluster consist of terms like text mining, data mining, data visualisation, sentiment analysis, user-generated content, user experience, knowledge discovery, forecasting, regression analysis, human computer interaction, information systems, information management, predictive analytics, decision making, time series analysis, social media analysis, social networking, marketing, social media platforms, network analysis and big data.",
